data.description: Discover your dream home in a prime location! This stunning property with 5 bedrooms and 3 baths is tailor-made for discerning people seeking the perfect blend of modern living and entertainment. Step into the spacious open floor plan that promises endless opportunities for hosting and relaxing with family and friends. The kitchen is a chef's paradise, featuring a roomy layout, a convenient kitchen island, and a breakfast bar for delightful culinary experiences. Imagine whipping up gourmet meals while staying connected to your loved ones in the adjoining living space, offering breathtaking views of the backyard. Speaking of the backyard, it's an absolute paradise! Lounge by the inviting pool complete with a thrilling slide for those fun-filled summer days. As night falls, gather around the enchanting fire pit, creating cherished memories with friends and loved ones. The entire backyard boasts a sophisticated stone covering, combining elegance with easy maintenance. But the perks don't stop there! This fantastic home is conveniently located very close to the Coachella festival site. Experience the thrill of being just moments away from one of the most iconic music and cultural events in the world. Your ideal lifestyle awaits you in this fabulous property. Whether you're hosting gatherings, enjoying quality family time, or exploring the vibrant festival scene nearby, this home offers it all.
